basic.floral_language:
Pachira macrocarpa
Floriography: luck, prosperity, prosperity 
Money tree is evergreen foliage plants, because of its meaning “Good luck and happiness to you”, is favored by the public. 
Money tree plant stature is beautiful. It has strong branches, leaves are green, and oblong, arranged in small palm and is full of vitality. The lush leaves, also have the effect of purify air, so they can be used for indoor beautification. 
Money tree is resistant to shade, is suitable for the scattered light in the bright place. With proper maintenance, it also can be flowering, and flowers color are red, white or light yellow.
basic.blooming: Foliage plants, sometimes flowering in April-May, red, white, light yellow flowers

maintenance.soil: Peat mixed with coarse sand soil
maintenance.sunlight: Like sunshine, but have strong resistant to shade, under half shade for better care in summer
maintenance.watering: Moderately resistant to drought, water thoroughly when soil is dry, may spray water in the air to keep moist
maintenance.fertilization: Dilute fertilizers following instructions, apply 1-2 times monthly in spring and autumn
maintenance.pruning: Remove dead and yellowish leaves timely
